                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_107027">Clapcote</placeName>.
                            
                            <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Badecok</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_107073">W<supplied>allingford</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName> grants to <persName>
                           <forename>Walter</forename> 
                           <surname>Crypse</surname>
                        </persName> a toft with arable land adjacent, lying between the said Walterâ€™s land on the north, and the garden which belonged to <persName>Sir <forename>William</forename> de <surname>Bereford</surname>
                        </persName> by <placeName type="castle" key="place_107073">Wallingford castle</placeName> on the south, in the village of <placeName key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </placeName>, reaching from the high road on the west to the barbican of the castle on the east. It is 28 feet wide by the road, and 68 feet by the barbican; length 55 and 58 feet.
                            Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>Louches</surname>
                        </persName>: 
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Gilbert</forename> du <surname>char</surname>
                        </persName>, 
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Thomas</forename> 
                           <surname>Aleyn</surname>
                        </persName>,
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Simon</forename> 
                           <surname>Kenelm</surname>
                        </persName>, 
                            <persName>
                           <forename>Nicholas</forename> le <surname>coupere</surname>
                        </persName>. 
                            Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_107027">C<supplied>lapcote</supplied>
                        </placeName>. 
                            <origDate when="1331-02-06">
                           <supplied>6 Feb. 1331.</supplied>
                        </origDate>
                        </p>
